comments: One of the worst TA\'s ever! She does not care for her students. Quiz grade averages have been insanely low. Hard grader. She only comes to discussion for the money only. She needs to go away!
i don\'t always go to her class often however, i do have to check on Wiley Plus to see whether did she post up new hw(unlimited attempts).so far i received a C without trying.

I am actually in her class right now and she seems to be a little all over the place. She totally sucks at multiplying. She does not correct you, she lets the class as a whole correct you. Homework is online on Wiley Plus,(Don\'t buy the book). As for now, class seems to be going good though. I really think she has like a lazy eye or something.

Ms. Yaggie is a grad student so she is still learning but I still think she should rethink teaching. She tries to be helpful, but I think she is unorganized and kind of an airhead. Be prepared for a lot of ridiculousness in her class.
